\f40\fs20\insrsid13633421\charrsid10958903  We must not however, if my interpretation is right, understand his thes
is there is no correct living in a false world to imply that there is no intrinsic moral value in the world. There is some intrinsic moral value in the experience of having ineffable insights, and in the practical manifestation of this experience in acts 
of ethical resistance. This is the }{\i\f40\fs20\insrsid13633421\charrsid10958903 Gl\'fcck der Erkenntnis}{\f40\fs20\insrsid13633421\charrsid10958903  which is left to us. 
